  },
  "remediation": {
   "desc": "Enable **log file integrity validation** on all trails (`LogFileValidationEnabled=true`).\n\nEnforce **least privilege** on the logs bucket, retain and protect digest files (e.g., S3 Object Lock/MFA Delete), and monitor validation results to support **defense in depth**.",
   "references": [
    "https://hub.prowler.com/check/cloudtrail_log_file_validation_enabled"
   ]
  },
  "risk_details": "Without validation, adversaries can alter, forge, or delete audit entries without detection, compromising log **integrity** and non-repudiation.\n\nThis impairs investigations, enables alert evasion, and obscures unauthorized changes across regions or accounts.",
  "time": 1783301528,
  "time_dt": "2026-07-05T21:32:08.523936",
  "type_uid": 200401,
  "type_name": "Detection Finding: Create"
 },
