   "region": "us-east-1"
  },
  "remediation": {
   "desc": "Adopt **automated certificate lifecycle management**: prefer **ACM-issued certs with auto-renewal**, or integrate imports with an automated renewal/rotation pipeline. Track expirations with alerts, enforce **least privilege** for cert operations, remove unused certs, and test rollovers to avoid downtime.",
   "references": [
    "https://hub.prowler.com/check/acm_certificates_expiration_check"
   ]
  },
  "risk_details": "Expired or near-expiry **TLS certificates** can break handshakes, causing **service outages** and failed API calls (**availability**). Emergency fixes raise misconfiguration risk, enabling disabled verification or weak ciphers, which allows **MITM** and data exposure (**confidentiality**/**integrity**).",
  "time": 1783301528,
  "time_dt": "2026-07-05T21:32:08.523936",
  "type_uid": 200401,
  "type_name": "Detection Finding: Create"
 },
