   "created_time_dt": "2026-07-05T21:32:08.523936",
   "desc": "**AWS account contact information** is current for the **primary contact** and the **alternate contacts** for `security`, `billing`, and `operations`, with accurate email addresses and phone numbers.",
   "title": "AWS account contact information is current",
   "types": [
    "Software and Configuration Checks/Industry and Regulatory Standards/AWS Foundational Security Best Practices"
   ],
